article_id:2387,category_name:Events,title_name:Nightmare and Omega Difficulties Will Be Unlocked in the Stranded Scions Raid Event!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bd60684182bb515f8befa91c93e72a2f.png,message:<div>Nightmare and Omega difficulties will be unlocked for raid battles in the Stranded Scions raid event on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627884000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bd60684182bb515f8befa91c93e72a2f.png"></div><div>■Nightmare Difficulty<br>To challenge Nightmare difficulty, you must clear the Extra Raid Battle. The amount of otherworld fragments and getherwings required to challenge Nightmare difficulty and the drop rewards available from it are the same as Expert difficulty.<br><br>Once per day, when you clear Nightmare difficulty, you can get a Grand Bounty. The Grand Bounty you receive is randomly selected from a set of rewards.<br><br>■Omega Difficulty<br>To challenge Omega difficulty, you must clear the raid battle on Nightmare difficulty and complete episode 5 of the event story. Additionally, to unlock Omega difficulty, you must collect three omega keys. You can obtain one omega key from each type of emblem rewards: bronze emblems, silver emblems, and gold emblems.<br><br>・Omega Level 1 (Solo)<br>This quest is for solo play only. It will unlock when you clear the raid battle on Nightmare difficulty and complete episode 5 of the event story.<br><br>・Omega Level 1 (Raid)<br>This quest is for co-op play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 1 (Solo).<br><br>・Omega Level 2 (Solo)<br>This quest is for solo play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 1 (Raid).<br><br>・Omega Level 2 (Raid)<br>This quest is for co-op play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 2 (Solo).<br><br>・Omega Level 3 (Solo)<br>This quest is for solo play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 2 (Raid).<br><br>・Omega Level 3 (Raid)<br>This quest is for co-op play only and will unlock when you clear Omega Level 3 (Solo).<br><br>■Availability<br>Nightmare and Omega difficulties will be available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1627884000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1628747999"></span>.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1627884000,update_time1627439959